A rare complication.

517
00:29:41,046 --> 00:29:44,447
The nodules must not have
been detected during imaging.

518
00:29:44,482 --> 00:29:47,151
We can't use these lungs.

519
00:29:49,271 --> 00:29:51,188
We're done.

520
