Put them on ice.

522
00:30:01,966 --> 00:30:03,666
There's another option.

523
00:30:07,706 --> 00:30:09,150
This can't be over
before it starts.

524
00:30:09,174 --> 00:30:10,668
It's not. You've already
been established

525
00:30:10,692 --> 00:30:12,176
as lung donor matches.

526
00:30:12,211 --> 00:30:14,105
We are gonna use a lobe
of lung from each of you

527
00:30:14,129 --> 00:30:16,249
and the liver and
pancreas we just procured.

528
00:30:17,999 --> 00:30:20,633
- If you agree.
- Of course,

529
00:30:20,669 --> 00:30:22,113
but she'll only have
two lobes of lung.

530
00:30:22,137 --> 00:30:23,898
All she needs is
two lobes of lung.

531
00:30:23,922 --> 00:30:25,706
And they will expand over time.

532
00:30:25,741 --> 00:30:27,191
Better than her diseased ones.

533
00:30:27,226 --> 00:30:28,870
Much better than
her diseased ones.

534
00:30:28,894 --> 00:30:30,655
But they haven't been
prepped for surgery.

535
00:30:30,679 --> 00:30:32,390
They haven't fasted, they could
aspirate when they go under.

536
00:30:32,414 --> 00:30:34,864
Anesthesia can do a
rapid sequence intubation

537
00:30:34,900 --> 00:30:36,666
to limit the risk of aspiration.

538
00:30:36,701 --> 00:30:38,118
Let's get you both to pre-op.

539
00:30:38,153 --> 00:30:39,870
If we don't move forward,

540
00:30:39,905 --> 00:30:41,632
we may never have
another opportunity like this.

541
00:30:41,656 --> 00:30:44,324
You're our daughter, Elo.

542
00:30:44,359 --> 00:30:47,027
The board has agreed
to livestream the surgery,

543
00:30:47,062 --> 00:30:49,057
but only to Eloise's
med school classmates,

544
00:30:49,081 --> 00:30:51,009
- just a limited feed.
- Like she said,

545
00:30:51,033 --> 00:30:52,977
no matter what, it will
be a great learning tool.

546
00:30:53,001 --> 00:30:54,529
This just went from
an incredible long shot

547
00:30:54,553 --> 00:30:56,135
to virtually impossible.

548
00:30:56,171 --> 00:30:57,999
Well, then, we'd
better work a miracle.

549
00:30:58,023 --> 00:31:00,263
There's an entire family
in there counting on us.

550
00:31:02,194 --> 00:31:04,144
Hey, I'm on call for thoracic.

551
00:31:04,179 --> 00:31:05,190
Said you guys could use a hand.

552
00:31:05,214 --> 00:31:06,334
Welcome to the team, bro.

553
00:31:20,212 --> 00:31:21,995
Hmm.

554
00:31:22,030 --> 00:31:24,197
Diseased liver and
pancreas removed.

555
00:31:24,232 --> 00:31:26,149
So far, so good.

556
00:31:28,754 --> 00:31:31,674
Donor liver and pancreas,
ready for implantation.

557
00:31:43,268 --> 00:31:45,418
Mom and Dad are stable.

558
00:31:45,454 --> 00:31:48,071
Here we go.

559
00:31:54,579 --> 00:31:56,107
How many people
are watching this?

560
00:31:56,131 --> 00:31:57,781
Not many.

561
00:31:57,816 --> 00:31:59,932
Probably just the gunners.

562
00:32:15,083 --> 00:32:17,111
They're finishing the
liver and pancreas.

563
