We need the right
lower lobe of lung.

564
00:32:19,020 --> 00:32:21,082
The lobe's harder to
remove than we expected.

565
00:32:21,106 --> 00:32:24,958
Mom has some adhesions
to the chest wall. Stapler.

566
00:32:30,015 --> 00:32:32,416
Transecting the
segmental branches

567
00:32:32,451 --> 00:32:33,984
off the pulmonary artery.

568
00:32:35,804 --> 00:32:38,337
Get Dr. Austin. Now!

569
00:32:49,068 --> 00:32:51,951
One order of lung to go.

570
