transfusion protocol?

574
00:33:03,081 --> 00:33:06,110
Yes. I've been trying to
repair the pulmonary artery,

575
00:33:06,134 --> 00:33:07,295
but the damage is extensive.

576
00:33:07,319 --> 00:33:10,153
Artery forceps to me.

577
00:33:21,533 --> 00:33:24,734
Dr. Austin needs you
to implant the lung.

578
00:33:24,770 --> 00:33:26,564
- Where's Dr. Austin?
- He's helping with the mom.

579
00:33:26,588 --> 00:33:28,349
- She's bleeding out.
- What?

580
00:33:28,373 --> 00:33:29,723
You stay. I'll go.

581
00:33:43,205 --> 00:33:44,499
What's happening?

582
00:33:44,523 --> 00:33:46,006
It's impossible to see anything.

583
00:33:46,041 --> 00:33:47,757
We need to convert to open.

584
00:33:47,793 --> 00:33:49,125
10 blade.

585
00:33:50,128 --> 00:33:52,211
Retractor to Bell.

586
00:33:54,566 --> 00:33:57,100
Put your finger on
that proximal P.A.

587
00:33:58,103 --> 00:34:00,670
Getting the lung
out of the field

588
00:34:00,706 --> 00:34:02,422
will give us a better view.

589
00:34:02,457 --> 00:34:05,625
Looks like the lobe got damaged.

590
00:34:06,978 --> 00:34:09,195
Implant the lung with
Mina. I'll fix the bleed.

591
00:34:12,617 --> 00:34:16,185
3-0 Prolene.

592
00:34:16,221 --> 00:34:18,437
On my mark, let go
and I'll sew this up.

593
00:34:18,473 --> 00:34:20,193
- You ready?
- Yeah.

594
00:34:20,225 --> 00:34:22,609
Go.

595
00:34:22,644 --> 00:34:23,993
Suction. Lap.

596
00:34:26,831 --> 00:34:29,031
Had to check on a patient.

597
00:34:29,067 --> 00:34:31,567
- How we doing?
- Florence lost a lot of blood.

598
00:34:31,603 --> 00:34:34,036
- They're working to save her.
- Eloise?

599
00:34:34,072 --> 00:34:36,722
They're putting in Florence's
right lower lobe now,

600
00:34:36,758 --> 00:34:39,292
but it may be damaged.

601
00:34:40,962 --> 00:34:43,813
Eloise can't live
with only one lobe.

602
00:34:46,652 --> 00:34:48,634
Dad's lobe on
the left looks good.

603
00:34:48,670 --> 00:34:51,404
Mom's lobe on the right
shows some contusions.

604
00:34:51,439 --> 00:34:53,590
Let's hope this works.

